Package: upsanddowns
Type: Package
Title: Turns Data into Short Form Commentary for RMarkdown
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Francesca", "Bryden", , "francesca.bryden@dft.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Designed for use within RMarkdown commentary, this package provides simple commentary for percentages, percentage points and numerical values.
    Functions are highly customisable, allowing users to select a choice of descriptive words, rounding, and numerical formatting.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Imports: stringr, scales, purrr, dftutils, dplyr, lubridate
Remotes:
    department-for-transport-public/dftutils
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
